{"id": 1481, "genre": 1000, "title": "经过一个假期，你又看透了哪些旅游景点惯用路数？", "description": "看到这些宣传用语，我抱起钱包就跑。（题图来自：Pierre Pang and Elaine Tang ）", "record_count": 11910, "comment_count": 25, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170204130639YKe3z5Vnxkfyvt1b.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-02-05T17:00:42Z", "questions": [{"id": 1847, "title": "经过一个假期，你又看透了哪些旅游景点惯用路数？", "content": "你都熟知哪些旅游景点惯用路数？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 161414, "content": "偏远人少的地方就叫“世间最后一片净土”", "image": "img/option/option/201702041347217PlWk9m0D8TMcou3.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 161421, "content": "“最美”铁路线有二十几条，“最美”乡村二百多个", "image": "img/option/option/20170204133551r19XPIxNzFTouSkK.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 161422, "content": "本地赏樱圣地，“私藏了整个春天”，去了一共一棵树", "image": "img/option/option/20170204133615TgxdDa3lOZX1Np29.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 161423, "content": "“艳遇”大理、“艳遇”波斯，没遇着算谁的？", "image": "img/option/option/20170204135730A1UF9iokdzswBZNH.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 161424, "content": "“情侣旅游胜地”，标配是蹩脚心形建筑外加一堆锁", "image": "img/option/option/20170204133720cJz0gQlFLSu2hy7Y.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 161425, "content": "不光人少，连景点和各种服务都很少的“冷门旅行地”", "image": "img/option/option/20170204134224JCp0m6e4NQf3vkgc.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 161427, "content": "“一生必去的若干景点”=爸妈最爱的打卡景点", "image": "img/option/option/20170204134458hoPdOB5AGIiHgzk1.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 161428, "content": "网红景点的“本土版“：安吉北海道、深圳凯旋门", "image": "img/option/option/201702041346415vqufjNKX8wcxUA0.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}